Everybody wants to live a life in their own house with their set of requirements for how a house to be. Before buying a house, people look at certain features and estimate the price of the house in order to see if it is within their budget. In such scenarios, it would be easy if there are options to look at those features and see how much the current price is for the particular house. Also, people who like to sell the house, would be eager to know the value of their property. 